title: Essential Japanese: Speak Japanese with Confidence
description:
In this book you will find:

Over 1500 practical sentences for everyday use.
A glossary of over 200 terms and expressions.
Latest Japanese vocabulary and Japanese phrases for smart phones, social media and more.

Japanese characters (kana and kanji) as well as Latin script (romanji).
This beginner Japanese book will help you to quickly and easily learn Japanese. Your ability to read Japanese, write Japanese, speak Japanese, and comprehend Japanese will be vastly improved without having to take an entire Japanese language class.

Genre: Education
